OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776600665
OL,3,CNHS begins giving second dose of MenB
OL,4,Cvaccine after deadly Kent outbreak
OL,6,FPeople who received vaccinations
OL,7,Fagainst a meningitis variant after a
OL,8,Fdeadly outbreak in Kent are getting
OL,9,Ftheir second dose.
OL,11,FLast month, two students died and a
OL,12,Ffurther 19 were confirmed to have
OL,13,Fmeningitis B during the outbreak,
OL,14,Fwhich was linked to a nightclub in
OL,15,FCanterbury.
OL,17,FHealth officials responded by offering
OL,18,Fthousands of people antibiotics and
OL,19,Fvaccines in an effort to stem the
OL,20,Fspread of cases.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
