PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776600665
OL,3,CNHS begins giving second dose of MenB
OL,4,Cvaccine after deadly Kent outbreak
OL,6,FAnyone who received a first dose of
OL,7,Fthe meningitis B vaccine four weeks
OL,8,Fago can book in for their second jab
OL,9,Ffrom Friday.
OL,11,FOfficials started vaccinating
OL,12,FUniversity of Kent students on
OL,13,FWednesday March 18.
OL,15,FThe following day, on a visit to the
OL,16,Fcampus, Health Secretary Wes Streeting
OL,17,Fsaid the programme would be expanded
OL,18,Fto more people, including sixth form
OL,19,Fpupils at four schools with known or
OL,20,Fsuspected cases of meningitis B.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
