OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776600665
OL,3,CNHS begins giving second dose of MenB
OL,4,Cvaccine after deadly Kent outbreak
OL,6,FThe NHS says a two-course dose is
OL,7,Fneeded for the "best, long-lasting
OL,8,Fprotection".
OL,10,FAppointment clinics are being offered
OL,11,Fat a number of locations across Kent,
OL,12,Fincluding Faversham and Ashford.
OL,14,FPupils from schools affected by the
OL,15,Foutbreak in years 11, 12 and 13 will
OL,16,Falso be offered a second vaccine at
OL,17,Ftheir school.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
